snippet.title: Resident Evil 4 VR Mode - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience the ultimate immersive experience as Leon S. Kennedy takes on a grueling rescue mission!
Coming as free DLC for the PlayStation®5 version of Resident Evil 4.
https://www.residentevil.com/re4/

Release date: TBD
